## CRITICAL: True/False Activity Structure (activity_true_false)

**Question structure:**
- Use `fieldset` elements with `border-0 m-0 p-0` classes for each question
- Question content in `legend` with flex layout: `<div class="flex gap-4">`
- Number each question: `<p class="font-semibold activity-text" data-id="...">1.</p>`
- Question text as separate span with `data-id`

**Radio button styling:**
- Hidden radio inputs: `class="sr-only peer"`
- Custom styled labels with `cursor-pointer` and hover effects
- Button appearance: `px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-200 peer-checked:bg-blue-500 peer-checked:text-white`
- Focus states: `peer-focus:ring-2 peer-focus:ring-blue-400 peer-focus:ring-offset-2`
- Minimum width for consistency: `min-w-[60px] text-center`

**Required attributes:**
- Each question needs one statement identifier (e.g., `item-1`) and BOTH radio inputs for that question must share that same `data-activity-item`
- Only render "Yes"/"No" text if matching provided text IDs exist; otherwise use non-text markers/icons and keep labels in `aria-label`
- Proper `name` attributes to group radio buttons per question

Example true/false activity:
```html
<section class="space-y-4 lg:w-3/4 mx-auto" data-section-type="activity_true_false" data-section-id="SECTION_ID_FROM_INPUT" role="activity">
  <!-- Title and image -->
  <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl text-center mb-4" data-id="text-19-0">Activity Title</h1>
  <img class="w-full max-w-64 mx-auto block mb-4 rounded-lg" data-id="img-19-0" src="images/image.jpg" alt="Description">

  <!-- Instructions -->
  <p class="mb-4 text-center mb-8">
    <i class="fas fa-pen-to-square text-blue-700 mr-2"></i>
    <span data-id="text-19-2">Instructions here</span>
  </p>

  <div class="activity-text">
    <!-- Question 1 -->
    <fieldset class="border-0 m-0 p-0 activity-text">
      <legend class="mb-3">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <p class="font-semibold activity-text" data-id="text-19-3">1.</p>
          <span data-id="text-19-4">Question text here?</span>
        </div>
      </legend>

      <div class="flex space-x-4 ml-8">
        <label for="question1-yes" class="relative flex items-center cursor-pointer group">
          <input id="question1-yes" name="question1" tabindex="0" type="radio" value="true"
                 data-activity-item="item-1" class="sr-only peer">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-200 peer-checked:bg-blue-500 peer-checked:text-white peer-focus:ring-2 peer-focus:ring-blue-400 peer-focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors min-w-[60px] text-center relative">
            <span data-id="text-19-25">Yes</span>
            <span class="validation-mark absolute right-0 top-0 transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden"></span>
          </div>
        </label>
        <label for="question1-no" class="relative flex items-center cursor-pointer group">
          <input id="question1-no" name="question1" tabindex="0" type="radio" value="false"
                 data-activity-item="item-1" class="sr-only peer">
          <div class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-200 peer-checked:bg-blue-500 peer-checked:text-white peer-focus:ring-2 peer-focus:ring-blue-400 peer-focus:ring-offset-2 transition-colors min-w-[60px] text-center relative">
            <span data-id="text-19-26">No</span>
            <span class="validation-mark absolute right-0 top-0 transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 hidden"></span>
          </div>
        </label>
      </div>
    </fieldset>

    <!-- Additional questions follow same pattern -->
  </div>

  <!-- Accessibility announcements -->
  <div id="validation-results-announcement" class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="assertive"></div>
  <div id="keyboard-action-announcement" class="sr-only" role="status" aria-live="polite"></div>
</section>
```

**Key requirements:**
- Wrap all questions in `<div class="activity-text">`
- Use `fieldset` with `border-0 m-0 p-0` for semantic grouping
- Question numbers and text must have separate `data-id` attributes
- Radio buttons need `sr-only peer` class for custom styling
- Include `validation-mark` span for JavaScript feedback
- Add accessibility announcements at the end
- Use consistent spacing with `ml-8` for radio button indentation
- Include proper focus and hover states for accessibility
